data.description: If you're looking for a beautiful and spacious home in the popular subdivision of Hidden Meadows of Northport, then take a hard look at this property. There's 5 beds, 4 full baths and hardwoods throughout on the main. The open layout from kitchen to living room the peers into the private, fenced in backyard which adjoins Hidden Meadows Golf Course. Additionally, on the main, there's a bedroom, laundry, and full bath. Upstairs you'll find the master, den, and remaining bedroom and baths. The exterior of this home was cleaned from top to bottom by a popular soft wash company in Birmingham and new HVAC installed within the year. The location is fantastic with being so close to Hwy 82, a few minutes grocery and home improvement stores and about 10 miles to University of Alabama.
